Package com.opengamma.strata.pricer.swaption

Calculators for swaptions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BlackVolatilitySwaptionProvider
    Volatility environment for swaption in the log-normal or Black model.
    NormalVolatilitySwaptionProvider
    Volatility environment for swaption in the normal or Bachelier model.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlackSwaptionCashParYieldProductPricer
    Pricer for swaption with par yield curve method of cash settlement in a log-normal or Black model on the swap rate.
    BlackSwaptionCashParYieldTradePricer
    Pricer for swaption trade with par yield curve method of cash settlement in log-normal or Black model on the swap rate.
    BlackSwaptionPhysicalProductPricer
    Pricer for swaption with physical settlement in a log-normal or Black model on the swap rate.
    BlackSwaptionPhysicalTradePricer
    Pricer for swaption trade with physical settlement in log-normal or Black model on the swap rate.
    BlackVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider
    Volatility environment for swaptions in the log-normal or Black model.
    BlackVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider.Meta
    The meta-bean for BlackVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider.
    NormalSwaptionCashParYieldProductPricer
    Pricer for swaption with par yield curve method of cash settlement in a normal model on the swap rate.
    NormalSwaptionCashParYieldTradePricer
    Pricer for swaption trade with par yield curve method of cash settlement in a normal model on the swap rate.
    NormalSwaptionPhysicalProductPricer
    Pricer for swaption with physical settlement in a normal model on the swap rate.
    NormalSwaptionPhysicalTradePricer
    Pricer for swaption trade with physical settlement in a normal model on the swap rate.
    NormalVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider
    Volatility environment for swaptions in the normal or Bachelier model.
    NormalVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider.Meta
    The meta-bean for NormalVolatilityExpiryTenorSwaptionProvider.
    SabrSwaptionCashParYieldProductPricer
    Pricer for swaption with par yield curve method of cash settlement in SABR model.
    SabrSwaptionCashParYieldTradePricer
    Pricer for swaption trade with par yield curve method of cash settlement in SABR model.
    SabrSwaptionPhysicalProductPricer
    Pricer for swaption with physical settlement in SABR model on the swap rate.
    SabrSwaptionPhysicalTradePricer
    Pricer for swaption trade with physical settlement in SABR model.
    SabrVolatilitySwaptionProvider
    Volatility environment for swaptions in SABR model.
    SabrVolatilitySwaptionProvider.Meta
    The meta-bean for SabrVolatilitySwaptionProvider.
